{"tid":1281891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打擊廢老 成為習慣]全部人入黎同我下載1823 APP","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T09:02:00.000Z","uid":57328,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"c84fe0b83f8e3f8dda3fd8b23fbb67e8aa8c6c07","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>iOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?mt=8&amp;l=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Ftell-me-1823%2Fid426069047%3Fmt%3D8%26l%3Dzh&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=9a694fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/tell-me-1823/id426069047?mt=8&amp;l=zh</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823&amp;hl=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dgov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823%26hl%3Dzh&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=af834395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=gov.hk.ogcio.tellme1823&amp;hl=zh</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家係未見到廢老都眼火爆，咁請你地每個人將怒火化為力量，將投訴廢老變成每日習慣，搞到佢地雞犬不寧。 好多巴打已經做緊，你都一齊加入啦！<br />\n<br />\n用法：<br />\n1. 下載APP<br />\n2. 投訴<br />\n3. 揀地點, 講發生咩事<br />\n4. 有專人幫你跟進, 一定要回覆你<br />\n<br />\n可以投訴既事項 (仲有更多):<br />\n1. 廢老非法聚賭<br />\n2. 阻街<br />\n3. 非法排污, 無牌賣酒<br />\n4. 違例泊車<br />\n5. 行乞<br />\n6. 非法勞工<br />\n7. 非法擺賣<br />\n8. 破壞環境<br />\n9. 破壞公物<br />\n10. 大媽/街站嘈音滋擾<br />\n11. 違法掛banner<br />\netc.<br />\n<br />\n總知你睇唔過眼, 覺得佢犯法就投訴得 <br />\n<br />\n由今日起，我會玩殘班死廢佬<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1266771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1266771</a>"},{"pid":"97da773d885865e8daf7fa179318081b918bbe2f","tid":1281891,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe7315761201b397513ecf1e28374d01efd47050","tid":1281891,"uid":260627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:58:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e05d24c4e2f2c643a0bcef38eadb472de066b800","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCosJ5S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCosJ5S.png&h=28f41711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n禁煙電郵<br />\n<br />\n由於違例吸煙是一瞬間的行為，執法人員難以在短時間內到場執法。因此，如你在禁煙區看見有人違例吸煙，你可即時向該場所的管理人投訴，要求場所管理人執行禁煙條例。<br />\n<br />\n如違例吸煙的情況仍然繼續在該場所發生，你可考慮向衞生署控煙酒辦公室作出投訴（電話：2961 8823／傳真：2575 8944／電郵： tobaccocontrol@dh.gov.hk）。控煙酒辦會跟進調查個案，並安排巡查執法。"},{"pid":"5233b92a06fb1ee485293d0f13927ec3a6c57d7a","tid":1281891,"uid":197213,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"香港要重獲投訴之都既美譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f2960c5ba70d72c8a57f9552518a34d5943242","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/YuenLongKsir/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FYuenLongKsir%2F&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=ff51cce5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/YuenLongKsir/</a><br />\n<br />\n可參考專業投訴人士k sir"},{"pid":"cd68fee6b76ad4c7d350e2f2ae5cd538502c1e6b","tid":1281891,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59bb50140be2734948ebd788707986613d056b3","tid":1281891,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201