edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a2483b2181c7cdefa58ccd106a016ebb40539c9e","tid":1281891,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:37:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"dbac20d99e0aee9b915a0bbc4aa9d49ee7020f8d","tid":1281891,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:39:38.000Z","msg":"1. 廢老非法聚賭<br />\n2. 阻街<br />\n3. 非法排污, 無牌賣酒<br />\n4. 違例泊車<br />\n5. 行乞<br />\n6. 非法勞工<br />\n7. 非法擺賣<br />\n8. 破壞環境<br />\n9. 破壞公物<br />\n10. 大媽/街站嘈音滋擾<br />\n11. 違法掛banner<br />\n12. 懷疑黑社會活動"},{"pid":"698189769ee4a5971c504c74d8d7b2f00fe92f64","tid":1281891,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da704a049f2c6af39a768c9d3b31bd06dcdbd4c4","tid":1281891,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"應該集中犬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗, 只要增加敵人生活成本就得"},{"pid":"7229f7165a1f1d0e0eb771a07212b5f42ba17414","tid":1281891,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb5d78d3b5609fcf2efeab28cbdeb0e183a20ba4","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4af1bebf99cc0eb47d3b4dedbb2a5a73575713","tid":1281891,"uid":79306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afc804f0c7cec8743b9232962a46fac0cca3b56b","tid":1281891,"uid":41257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce121412bac76dc45eafd17f74536c3d36c7f287","tid":1281891,"uid":51761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"已 dl,一見到就report"},{"pid":"90791f950275058a7069525defeb8f266923a510","tid":1281891,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37e1dc04bb54ad3ea743b76863a22e329d1f511e","tid":1281891,"uid":12171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"住用處所及公眾地方發出的噪音<br />\n《噪音管制條例》訂有管制條文，防止住戶和公眾地方發出的噪音滋擾鄰舍。該 條例訂有一項一般條文，管制此類在晚上或公眾假期發出的擾人噪音。該條例又賦權當局 管制包括源自樂器、動物、雀鳥、遊戲或經營業務，於日間或夜間任何時間在住戶和公眾 地方發出的噪音。這些條文主要由警務處負責執行。<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好投訴錯部門呀，同時要保護好自己個人資料，要求1823唔好將自己既資料交俾警方，而且要求書面回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e4410b2907cddc407380cda592fcb0531d954c","tid":1281891,"uid":197958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"雲海 陳雲海 公開投訴政府部門心法：<br />\n<br />\n收到投訴，部份公務員慣常「此乃機密，不便透露」嚇窒市民，跟着以下步驟，自能見招拆招。<br />\n1. 問對方全名及職級。<br />\n2. 唔對路，即問上司全名。<br />\n3. 遭拒絕，同佢講所有政府部門的上級名字及職級都可公開，非機密。<br />\n4. 感被耍，找其部門的資料公開專員。<br />\n5. 再被耍，即問其全名、職級及直線電話。<br />\n6. 再找部門主管。<br />\n7. 部門主管玩嘢，你就把前線、公開資料專員及部門主管送到申訴專員公署。<br />\n8. 跟申訴專員講明三個單位都處理失當，要求跟進。"},{"pid":"a2cde365e985e77868dcbbbc9f997ca6795b1d6f","tid":1281891,"uid":11643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"996c264277860d4ea0c02607b557e8f8d30348d2","tid":1281891,"uid":71469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8140a4248956ac70d68e9d923b4c699c0a776e6c","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce121412bac76dc45eafd17f74536c3d36c7f287","tid":1281891,"uid":51761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"已 dl,一見到就report"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我已成為習慣"},{"pid":"e0b79d17238049f68acb62686666879114dd2bad","tid":1281891,"uid":57161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c3708628dd4a7c36a2c013d89cc07bd93ea472","tid":1281891,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊營造美好香港"},{"pid":"2977b488794c335fd65eead756c8f62cd9eb6e30","tid":1281891,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c7eac6ac1d9cab4b580dd84709343c4925a2f5","tid":1281891,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98516e44f8aef10fb2fdecf9c4d273dd5ba193ae","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:42:50.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"71ee069588b6e4fa4be17d769dcd293052c09100","tid":1281891,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T23:46:05.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"560f76425d1da252be775ec35c7f763ea23ffa16","tid":1281891,"uid":28728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:15:57.000Z","msg":"我要投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74af3275b926be141d85180f5e87e4a2a70a6927","tid":1281891,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:58:47.000Z","msg":"一日一違泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da15264bf666fa550f0b7c54cde3df5c4567a226","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"有野講"},{"pid":"6bdaa0c6f85e44a141d9d33ff91ddab1b85bae9f","tid":1281891,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48db9b29974f6f86b0f00d3f88ab7dea10bab182","tid":1281891,"uid":18258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"可以參考番呢2個post <br />\n<br />\n做政府多年，發現識用正確方法，鬧政府、屌政府的香港人非常少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/625096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/625096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港人多走一步，初用1823 app有感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/668165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/668165</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5da68a5ea4836b3c074d51e7eae14a1b23f9365","tid":1281891,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"一日一違泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161426a43a9b0d82af0ea1fdc1682c81b33189bf","tid":1281891,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f198e127b3923fd7f66c038adcdeddefe1807c97","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f16b1a298c2ea65fcb7e627fd04e81cdf485c7","tid":1281891,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:38:16.000Z","msg":"大家繼續努力超合作運動<br />\n今日已經6單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57e1f971294a42a70001d64d017c402df0e0353","tid":1281891,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f16b1a298c2ea65fcb7e627fd04e81cdf485c7","tid":1281891,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":